			 2014</header-in-text>
            </quote> and inserting <quote>
              <header-in-text level="subsection" style="OLC">January 1, 2015</header-in-text>
            </quote>.</text>
				</paragraph>
        <paragraph id="idbfb50d11b4e24c44aa4eb567a2d9cc49">
          <enum>(2)</enum>
          <text>The heading for
			 <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Internal Revenue Code of 1986/s:168/ss:k/p:2/sp:B/cl:ii">clause (ii) of section 168(k)(2)(B) of such Code</cato:entity-ref> is amended by striking
			 <quote>
