			 2014</header-in-text>
            </quote> and inserting <quote>
              <header-in-text level="clause" style="OLC">Pre-january 1, 2015</header-in-text>
            </quote>.</text>
				</paragraph>
        <paragraph id="idE3E0581942D24E9DB32D6E729BEA97E5">
          <enum>(3)</enum>
          <text>
            <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Internal Revenue Code of 1986/s:168/ss:k/p:4/sp:D">Section
			 168(k)(4)(D)</cato:entity-ref> is amended by striking <quote>and</quote> at the end of <cato:entity-ref xmlns:cato="http://namespaces.cato.org/catoxml" entity-type="act" value="Internal Revenue Code of 1986/s:168/ss:k/p:4/sp:D/cl:ii">clause
