              <text>by substituting
				<quote>January 1, 2014</quote> for <quote>January 1, 2015</quote> in clause (i)
				thereof,
				and</text>
						</subparagraph>
            <after-quoted-block>.</after-quoted-block>
          </quoted-block>
				</paragraph>
